Description_lang: Ragnaros creates a Magma Trap at the target location.  When the Magma Trap is triggered it will cause a Magma Trap Eruption, inflicting $98175s1 Fire damage to all enemies, and knocking the enemy that triggered the Magma Trap up extremely high into the air.
